This Privacy Policy describes how the "miniNotes" app collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our mobile application. By using the App, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect

User-Generated Content: The App allows you to create and store notes. This includes text, images, links, formatting and any other content that you input into the app.

Usage Data: We do not collect or have access to user's data.

Device Information: We do not collect any information related to your device.

Advertising Data: The Google Mobile Ads SDK is used to display banner ads and interstitial ads, it may collect information to show relevant ads, please review Google ad policy for more information.

2. How We Use Your Information

Display ads: The ad-related data is used to show personalized ads by Google.

App Analytics: We do not use usage data for any other analytics.

3. How We Share Your Information

- We will not sell or share your personal information with third parties for advertising purposes.

Law Enforcement: We may disclose information to comply with the law or legal processes, or to protect our rights.

4. Data Storage and Security

Local Storage: Your notes and other data are stored locally on your device using a local database. The data is saved locally.

Data Backup: The text and tags data are stored on your local storage.

Data Export/Import: You can share your notes via any channel available on your device as plain text, we do not support importing or exporting of notes using any other form.

6. Children's Privacy

This App is designed for general use and can be used by any age group. Our app does not contain any content against the policy. Though app contains ads so its recommended to 13+ age group.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page. You should review this Privacy Policy periodically for changes.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at iumarafzalkhan@gmail.com.
